          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Unlike fast-fashion bikinis that lose their shape after a few wears, our sustainable string bikinis are built to last - retaining their colour, fit, and comfort season after season. The tie-side design gives you the flexibility to adjust your fit on the go, while our seamless, double-lined construction ensures a smooth, flattering look from every angle.</p><p>From surf-ready string bikinis that won’t let you down in the water to minimalist tie-side bikinis perfect for tanning, this collection has something for every beach day. Each piece is ethically handmade in Bali, supporting fair wages and responsible manufacturing, so you can feel good about every wear.</p><p>Find your perfect string bikini and experience the comfort, style, and sustainability that Ocean Soul Swimwear is known for.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
