        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Choose Our String Bikinis?",
        "text": "<p>A string bikini might seem like a simple design, but the right one can completely transform how you feel at the beach. Our bikinis are designed to give you adjustability and style without sacrificing quality or performance.<br/> Customise your fit with tie sides and halter neck straps for comfort and security.<br/> Double-lined fabric offers coverage and a smooth silhouette that stays in place.<br/> Premium Italian recycled fabric is soft on your skin and gentle on the planet.<br/> Built-in sun protection keeps your skin safe during long days outdoors.<br/> Perfect for mixing and matching with any of our bikini bottoms or rash vests.<br/></p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
