        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Performance Meets Style",
        "text": "<p>Our string bikinis are designed for women who want freedom of movement and timeless style. They’re surf-tested to ensure they won’t shift during active water sports, but they’re also light, breathable, and perfect for relaxed sunbathing.</p><p>Tested in the waves to ensure minimal movement and maximum comfort.</p><p>Designed for both saltwater and pool wear without losing shape or colour.</p><p>Move from beach to bar without feeling damp or weighed down. </p>",
