        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 550,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Sustainability Without Compromise",
        "text": "<p>Ocean Soul Swimwear is committed to creating eco-friendly string bikinis that are as sustainable as they are stylish.</p><p>Made from ECONYL® regenerated nylon sourced from ocean waste like fishing nets.</p><p>We avoid overproduction to reduce waste.</p><p>Handmade in Bali by skilled artisans earning fair wages.<br/></p><p>By choosing a sustainable string bikini, you’re making a choice that’s better for the planet and for the people who make your swimwear.</p>",
